<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>OSMBMOT Certificate | BitcoinVersus.Tech</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #2ffa06;
      --shell: #34f104;
      --paper: #10130f;
      --paper-2: #14181c;
      --line: rgba(1, 3, 0, 0.18);
      --line-soft: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --neon: #30f808c7;
      --neon-soft: #30f808c7;
      --white: #e8ebe8;
      --muted: #aeb7bf;
      --silver: #dfe6ec;
      --ink: #fafffa;
      --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42), 0 0 24px rgba(57, 255, 20, 0.08);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Courier New", "Lucida Console", Monaco, monospace;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(57,255,20,0.08), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #010101 0%, #050505 100%);
      color: var(--white);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .wrap {
      max-width: 1260px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .brand .site {
      color: var(--neon);
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      text-transform: none;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
      text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(57,255,20,0.28);
    }

    .btn {
      border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.28);
      color: var(--neon);
      background: rgba(57,255,20,0.06);
      padding: 11px 16px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.18s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .cert-shell {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(8,8,8,0.98), rgba(5,5,5,0.98));
      border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.14);
      border-radius: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .cert-shell::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 100% 0%, rgba(57,255,20,0.08), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 0% 100%, rgba(57,255,20,0.05), transparent 26%),
        repeating-linear-gradient(
          180deg,
          rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 0px,
          rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 1px,
          transparent 1px,
          transparent 5px
        );
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .cert {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      min-height: 880px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(57,255,20,0.05), transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, var(--paper) 0%, var(--paper-2) 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .gridline {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 36px 36px;
      mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 35%, transparent 85%);
      -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at center, black 35%, transparent 85%);
      opacity: 0.28;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .top {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 36px 36px 22px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .logo-box {
      width: 170px;
      height: 230px;
      justify-self: center;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      justify-content: center;
      background: transparent;
      border: 0;
      box-shadow: none;
      padding: 0;
      overflow: visible;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .pixel-handheld {
      width: 170px;
      height: 230px;
      display: block;
      image-rendering: pixelated;
      image-rendering: crisp-edges;
      shape-rendering: crispEdges;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.34));
    }

    .eyebrow {
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--neon-soft);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
    }

    .title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--neon);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(57,255,20,0.28);
      max-width: 980px;
    }

    .meta-stack {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 980px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .meta-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(3px);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .meta-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--neon-soft);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
    }

    .meta-value {
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #f2f6fa;
      line-height: 1.45;
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .center-band {
      margin: 8px 36px 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(57,255,20,0.16);
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(57,255,20,0.08), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
    }

    .center-band-inner {
      display: block;
    }

    .recipient-panel {
      padding: 30px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-right: 0;
    }

    .recipient-name {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4vw, 3.6rem);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #30f808c7;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      width: 100%;
      font-family: "Ubuntu Mono", monospace;
    }

    .recipient-text {
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      color: #ffffff;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 820px;
      text-align: center;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
    }

    .bottom-grid {
      padding: 26px 36px 36px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 24px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .panel {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      border-radius: 22px;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .panel-title {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      color: var(--neon-soft);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
    }

    .desc {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #c2cbd3;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
    }

    .signature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .sig-card {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      padding-top: 14px;
    }

    .sig-script {
      font-family: "Brush Script MT", "Segoe Script", "Lucida Handwriting", cursive;
      font-size: 2.15rem;
      color: var(--neon);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(57,255,20,0.24), 0 0 20px rgba(57,255,20,0.12);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .sig-name {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #d9e0e7;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .verify-box {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .verify-line {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #d2dae2;
    }

    .verify-line span:first-child {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .verify-site {
      margin-top: 6px;
      color: var(--neon);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      word-break: break-word;
      font-family: Consolas, monospace;
    }

    .footnote {
      padding: 0 36px 30px;
      color: #86919c;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1020px) {
      .meta-stack {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        max-width: 420px;
      }

      .bottom-grid,
      .signature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .top {
        padding: 28px 24px 18px;
      }

      .center-band {
        margin: 8px 24px 0;
      }

      .bottom-grid,
      .footnote {
        padding-left: 24px;
        padding-right: 24px;
      }
    }

    @media print {
      body {
        background: #000;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .topbar {
        display: none;
      }

      .cert-shell {
        border: none;
        border-radius: 0;
        box-shadow: none;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .cert {
        border-radius: 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="topbar">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="site">BitcoinVersus.tech</div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn" onclick="window.print()">Print / Save PDF</button>
    </div>

    <section class="cert-shell">
      <article class="cert">
        <div class="gridline"></div>

        <section class="top">
          <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; align-items:center; width:100%;">
            <h1 class="title"><span>Open Source Master Bitcoin Mining Operations Technician Certification</span></h1>
          </div>

          <div class="logo-box">
            <svg class="pixel-handheld" viewBox="0 0 170 230" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-label="Pixel handheld badge">
              <defs>
                <linearGradient id="bodyGrad2" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#8dff74"/>
                  <stop offset="24%" stop-color="#43ef22"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#118b0d"/>
                </linearGradient>
                <linearGradient id="bezelGrad2" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#5a5d67"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#2f3238"/>
                </linearGradient>
                <linearGradient id="screenGrad2" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#0f1010"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#000000"/>
                </linearGradient>
                <linearGradient id="btnGrad2" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
                  <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1d1f1d"/>
                  <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#000000"/>
                </linearGradient>
                <pattern id="scan2" width="4" height="4" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                  <rect width="4" height="2" fill="#39ff14" opacity="0.08"/>
                </pattern>
              </defs>

              <rect x="18" y="10" width="134" height="198" rx="8" fill="url(#bodyGrad2)" stroke="#363a36" stroke-width="3"/>
              <rect x="18" y="10" width="134" height="198" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.10)" stroke-width="1"/>

              <text x="85" y="24" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#081108" font-family="Consolas, monospace" font-weight="700">BitcoinVersus.tech</text>

              <rect x="31" y="36" width="108" height="104" rx="6" fill="url(#bezelGrad2)" stroke="#24272c" stroke-width="2"/>
              <rect x="35" y="40" width="100" height="96" rx="4" fill="none" stroke="#7a7f88" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.55"/>
              <rect x="39" y="45" width="92" height="86" rx="4" fill="url(#screenGrad2)" stroke="#30422a" stroke-width="2"/>
              <rect x="39" y="45" width="92" height="86" rx="4" fill="url(#scan2)" opacity="0.72"/>

              <text x="85" y="79" text-anchor="middle" font-size="16" letter-spacing="1.1" fill="#39ff14" font-family="Consolas, monospace" font-weight="700">OSMBMOT</text>
              <text x="85" y="98" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.2" fill="#39ff14" font-family="Consolas, monospace" font-weight="700">BITCOIN MINING</text>
              <text x="85" y="108" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.2" fill="#39ff14" font-family="Consolas, monospace" font-weight="700">OPERATIONS TECH</text>
              <text x="85" y="118" text-anchor="middle" font-size="7.2" fill="#39ff14" font-family="Consolas, monospace" font-weight="700">MASTER BADGE</text>

              <rect x="36" y="164" width="34" height="12" rx="1" fill="url(#btnGrad2)" stroke="#0b0c0b" stroke-width="2"/>
              <rect x="47" y="153" width="12" height="34" rx="1" fill="url(#btnGrad2)" stroke="#0b0c0b" stroke-width="2"/>

              <circle cx="108" cy="168" r="9" fill="url(#btnGrad2)" stroke="#0b0c0b" stroke-width="2"/>
              <text x="108" y="171.5" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#39ff14" font-family="Consolas, monospace" font-weight="700">B</text>
              <circle cx="124" cy="182" r="9" fill="url(#btnGrad2)" stroke="#0b0c0b" stroke-width="2"/>
              <text x="124" y="185.5" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#39ff14" font-family="Consolas, monospace" font-weight="700">V</text>

              <rect x="104" y="198" width="18" height="4" rx="1" fill="#111111"/>
              <rect x="126" y="198" width="18" height="4" rx="1" fill="#111111"/>
            </svg>
          </div>

          <div class="meta-stack">
            <div class="meta-card">
              <div class="meta-label">Issue Date</div>
              <div class="meta-value">April 4, 2026</div>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-card">
              <div class="meta-label">Credential ID</div>
              <div class="meta-value">OSMBMOT BTCVT 2026 001 | Block 943682</div>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-card">
              <div class="meta-label">Proof of Work</div>
              <div class="meta-value">5,000+ Hours of Demonstrated Bitcoin Mining Operations</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="center-band">
          <div class="center-band-inner">
            <div class="recipient-panel">
              <div class="eyebrow">Awarded To</div>
              <div class="recipient-name">Matthan Burton</div>
              <div class="recipient-text">
                for demonstrating advanced applied competency across Bitcoin mining operations through multi site field work, ASIC deployment, firmware governance, machine troubleshooting, thermal management, electrical terminations, network cabling, asset control, infrastructure support, and operational execution in live mining environments.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bottom-grid">
          <div class="panel">
            <div class="panel-title">Program Summary</div>
            <div class="desc">
              The OSMBMOT certification documents demonstrated mastery in Bitcoin mining operations based on real work performed across industrial mining environments ranging from approximately 5 MW to 200 MW. The recipient has supported air cooled and immersion systems, handled ASIC deployment and replacement procedures, managed firmware environments, performed electrical and structured cabling work, supported network and switch related operations, maintained thermal reliability, executed preventative maintenance, and contributed to field leadership, documentation, and operational continuity under production conditions.
            </div>
            <div class="signature-grid">
              <div class="sig-card">
                <div class="sig-script">Matthan Burton</div>
                <div class="sig-name">
                  Founder and Senior Engineer<br />
                  BitcoinVersus.Tech<br />
                  Program Issuer
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="sig-card">
                <div class="sig-script">OSMBMOT</div>
                <div class="sig-name">Open Source Master Bitcoin Mining Operations Technician Certification</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="panel">
            <div class="panel-title">Proof of Verification</div>

            <div class="verify-box">
              <div class="verify-line"><span>Program Focus</span><span>Bitcoin Mining Operations</span></div>
              <div class="verify-line"><span>Credential Type</span><span>Open Source Certification</span></div>
              <div class="verify-line"><span>Competency Standard</span><span>Master Operations Technician</span></div>
              <div class="verify-line"><span>Issuer</span><span>BitcoinVersus.Tech</span></div>
              <div class="verify-line"><span>Status</span><span>Completed</span></div>
            </div>

            <div class="verify-site">BitcoinVersus.tech</div>

            <div class="desc" style="margin-top:16px;">
              This certificate records verifiable field experience and demonstrated technical work in Bitcoin mining operations. It does not represent a university degree, government license, or third party vendor credential. It exists to document open source professional mastery established through real operational work, technical execution, and sustained contribution under the BitcoinVersus.Tech certification framework.
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </article>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
